{% imageSection
   image="/images/staff/monty-janette-harlan.jpeg"
   alt="Monty Harlan - Executive Director"
   overlayPosition="center"
   height="md" /%}

## Monty Harlan - Executive Director

Monty has served as Executive Director of Camp Otyokwah, leading the camp's mission to challenge individuals to know and mature in Christ. Under his leadership, Camp Otyokwah has grown and deepened its impact as a ministry of the Churches of God General Conference, serving youth and families across Ohio and beyond.

**Email:** [monty@otyokwah.org](mailto:monty@otyokwah.org)
{% /twoColumns %}

---

{% twoColumns reverseOnMobile=true %}
## Connor Miller - Director of Operations

Connor oversees the day-to-day operations of Camp Otyokwah, ensuring our facilities and programs run smoothly. His attention to detail and commitment to excellence means every camper and guest experiences the best Camp Otyokwah has to offer.

**Email:** [connor@otyokwah.org](mailto:connor@otyokwah.org)

