## Rebekah Miller - Director of Operations

Rebekah works alongside Connor to manage camp operations and create welcoming experiences for every guest. Her warm hospitality and organizational skills ensure that every group that visits Camp Otyokwah feels at home from the moment they arrive.

**Email:** [rebekah@otyokwah.org](mailto:rebekah@otyokwah.org)
