{% twoColumns reverseOnMobile=true %}
## Jennifer Sherbahn - Program Director

Jennifer designs and leads our summer camp programs, creating meaningful experiences for campers of all ages. Her creativity and passion for discipleship shape the activities, worship, and teaching that make Camp Otyokwah summers unforgettable.

**Email:** [jennifer@otyokwah.org](mailto:jennifer@otyokwah.org)

